      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOCHINVAR GRACE (1) lines up chasing another win after scoring over 388m at this track in 22.03, set up by a brilliant early sectional. Winner at her latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Looks to have an edge on most of these. CHOPPER EXPRESS (3) is first up since finishing fourth (23.24) in a Free For All at The Gardens over 400m ten weeks ago. Form at this distance is sound. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. RAY FINKLE (2) is having his first look at this course. Last start placegetter off this draw when second (19.36) at Bulli. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Leading chance. BELTONE BOY (8) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
